bool IsPrime(int number)
{
    if(number==1)
        return false;
    for (int i=2; i<=sqrt(number); i++)
        if (number%i==0)
            return false;
    return true;
}
int sum(int num)
{
    int r, sum=0;
    while(num)
    {
        r=num%10;
        num/=10;
        sum+=r;
    }
    return sum;
}
